{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-10405/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-10405"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:04:05"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman stand facing each other on a stairacse."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-10405","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-10405"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1/c366a313-11a2-4700-86e0-65395a5549aa","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:01:39.434Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma, it turns out, has made the dress she is wearing. On the one hand, she is integrating herself into Reynolds’s life, house, and, most importantly, art. On the other hand, the dress is a copy of what Reynolds has already made for her (and it only elicits modest approval—“interesting”—from the tailor). She lacks a fully individual aesthetic beauty and remains under Reynolds’s control in this way.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:999.5749713302753,305.74326261467894,277.9472477064221,714.1879300458716"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1/0197ed40-4b8f-4f24-a6ef-7904531db242","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:02:00.168Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Reynolds realizes her dress is one she made herself, he has her come down to meet him on the stairs and present it to him to examine. He reiterates the power difference between them, and makes her seek his approval to validate her work, rather than allowing it to stand on its own, treating her as an equal.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10405/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1372.5731077981652,306.69151376146795,299.54415137614683,660.9826548165137"}}}]}]}]}